'''1854年大西洋飓风季'''确认存在五个[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]，其中三个曾[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]美国。有气象学家认为9月[[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]][[加尔维斯敦_(德克萨斯州)|加尔维斯敦]]附近有另一个热带气旋存在<ref name="Partagas">{{cite report | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/Landsea/Partagas/1851-1857/1854.pdf | title = Year 1854 | author = Jose F. Partagas | date = 1996 | work = Atlantic Oceanographic and Meteorological Laboratory | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304044026/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/Landsea/Partagas/1851-1857/1854.pdf | format = [[便携式文档格式|PDF]] | deadurl = no | publisher = [[美国国家海洋和大气管理局|National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration]] | pages = 21–26 | accessdate = 2016-11-17 | location = [[迈阿密|Miami]], [[佛罗里达州|Florida]] | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>，但[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]的[[大西洋飓风数据库|大西洋飓风正式数据库]]没有收录<ref name="HURDAT">{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | author2 = Hurricane Research Division | title = Atlantic hurricane best track (HURDAT version 2) | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-070616.txt | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2016-07-06 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161004150702/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-070616.txt | format = [[文本文件|TXT]] | accessdate = 2016-11-01 | archivedate = 2016-10-04 }}</ref>。第一号飓风是本季首场风暴，最早是在6月25日发现。第五号热带风暴是本季最后一个气旋，于10月22日失去踪影，都在[[大西洋|大西洋盆地]]每年绝大多数热带天气活动的时间范围内，不过本季没有任何两场风暴在同一时间共存。由于缺乏数据，有一个热带气旋的完整路径已经无从考证，只能确认风暴曾在某位置经过。

全季五个热带气旋中有三个达到飓风强度，其中一个还成为[[热带气旋等级|大型飓风]]，即在现代[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]下达到三级或以上标准{{#tag:ref|[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]于1971年面世<ref name="USA Today">{{cite news | author = Jack Williams | title = Hurricane scale invented to communicate storm danger | publisher = [[今日美国|USA Today]] | date = 2005-05-17 | accessdate = 2013-08-04 | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/hurricane/whscale.htm | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160324154907/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/hurricane/whscale.htm | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-24 }}</ref>，再对[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]大西洋飓风数据库的所有风暴追溯分级<ref>{{cite report | publisher = Hurricane Research Division | title = Chronological List of All Continental United States Hurricanes: 1851-2012 | date = 2013-06 | accessdate = 2016-11-10 | archivedate = 2016-05-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160503012801/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/All_U.S._Hurricanes.html | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/All_U.S._Hurricanes.html }}</ref>。|group="注"}}。第三号飓风的[[最大持续风速|最大持续风速]]达到每小时205公里，属三级飓风，是本季最强烈的风暴。气旋从[[乔治亚州|乔治亚州]]和[[南卡罗莱纳州|南卡罗莱纳州]]边界附近登陆，造成大面积破坏并夺走26条人命。第四号飓风袭击[[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]]沿海地区，导致四人遇难，损失数额约为两万美元（1854年美元）。第一号飓风也对德克萨斯州构成中等程度破坏。

这年飓风季低迷的活跃程度还经累积[[气旋能量指数|气旋能量指数]]反映出来，数值仅有31<ref>{{cite report | author = Hurricane Research Division | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2011-03 | title = Atlantic basin Comparison of Original and Revised HURDAT | accessdate = 2016-03-04 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304040342/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/Comparison_of_Original_and_Revised_HURDAT_mar11.html | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/Comparison_of_Original_and_Revised_HURDAT_mar11.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。大致来说，气旋能量指数通过飓风强度和持续时间计算，强度越高、持续时间越长的风暴，其指数也相应越高。只有在热带天气系统风速达到或超过每小时63公里（34[[节_(单位)|节]]）或热带风暴强度时才会计算该指数，并纳入全面的气象公告，并且[[亚热带气旋|亚热带气旋]]的指数不会计入累积数值。<ref>{{cite web |author=David Levinson |date=2008-08-20 |title=2005 Atlantic Ocean Tropical Cyclones |publisher=National Climatic Data Center |archiveurl=https://archive.li/20131105020723/http://www.ncdc.noaa.gov/oa/climate/research/2005/2005-atlantic-trop-cyclones.html |archivedate=2013-11-05 |deadurl=no |accessdate=2014-04-01 |url=http://www.ncdc.noaa.gov/oa/climate/research/2005/2005-atlantic-trop-cyclones.html }}</ref>
