=== 第三号飓风 ===
{{Infobox Hurricane Small
|Basin=Atl
|Image=1854 Atlantic hurricane 3 track.png
|Formed=9月7日
|Dissipated=9月12日
|1-min winds=110
|Pressure=938
}}
9月7日，“驯鹿号”（{{lang|en|Reindeer}}）[[双桅横帆船|双桅船]]在[[巴哈马|巴哈马]][[霍普敦|霍普敦]]（{{lang|en|Hope Town}}）以东约40公里海域发现飓风<ref name="Partagas" />，其最大持续风速为每小时205公里，最低气压938毫巴（百帕，27.7英寸汞柱），是本季最强烈的热带气旋。9月8日，风暴向西北方向移动并略有减弱，于{{lang|en|UTC}}晚上20点以风力时速185公里强度从乔治亚州[[圣凯瑟琳岛|圣凯瑟琳岛]]（{{lang|en|St. Catherines Island}}）附近登陆。9月9日清晨，气旋减弱成一级飓风，又在数小时后降级成热带风暴。此后，风暴加速向东北移动，并于9月10日从[[弗吉尼亚海滩|弗吉尼亚海滩]]附近返回大西洋。气旋重新增强，于9月11日再度成为飓风。风暴之后在快速向东移动期间再度减弱，最终在[[纽芬兰岛|纽芬兰岛]][[开普雷斯|开普雷斯]]（{{lang|en|Cape Race}}）东南方向约830公里洋面失去踪影<ref name="HURDAT" />。

佛罗里达州的烈风风场向南一直延伸到[[圣奥古斯丁_(佛罗里达州)|圣奥古斯丁]]。乔治亚州沿海地区受到显著影响，其中[[格林县_(乔治亚州)_(1777年)|格林县]][[圣西蒙斯_(乔治亚州)|圣西蒙斯]]（{{lang|en|St. Simons}}）及其北侧区域灾情尤为严重。约有45公顷水稻被毁，损失的稻谷约有6000[[蒲式耳|蒲式耳]]。[[萨凡纳|萨凡纳]]至南卡罗莱纳州[[查尔斯顿_(南卡罗莱纳州)|查尔斯顿]]沿海地区“潮水异常高涨”。<ref>{{cite report | archivedate = 2016-10-23 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161023182710/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/Landsea/history/index.html | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/Landsea/history/index.html | title = Chronological Listing of Tropical Cyclones affecting North Florida and Coastal Georgia 1565-1899 | author1 = Al Sandrik | author2 = Christopher W. Landsea | date = 2003-05 | work = Atlantic Oceanographic and Meteorological Laboratory | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | accessdate = 2016-11-18 }}</ref>乔治亚州的[[哈金森岛_(乔治亚州)|哈金森岛]]（{{lang|en|Hutchinson Island}}）被彻底淹没，萨凡纳东部也有大范围地区被淹。风暴潮令南卡罗莱纳州[[博福特_(南卡罗莱纳州)|博福特]]至[[乔治敦_(南卡罗莱纳州)|乔治敦]]的大范围沿海地区发生洪灾。狂风造成的破坏基本局限于树木倒塌。不过，查尔斯顿有幢两层高的木质建筑被毁，其他多幢建筑受到轻至中度损伤，主要是屋顶和围栏受到破坏。<ref>{{cite report | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304053453/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/Landsea/A%20Reanalysis%20of%20Five%2019th%20Century%20South%20Carolina%20Major%20Hurricanes.pdf | work = University of Northern Colorado | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/Landsea/A%20Reanalysis%20of%20Five%2019th%20Century%20South%20Carolina%20Major%20Hurricanes.pdf | title = A Reanalysis Of Five 19th Century South Carolina Major Hurricanes Using Local Data Sources | author = Douglas Owen Mayes | date = 1999 | publisher = Atlantic Oceanographic and Meteorological Laboratory | pages = 40–47 | accessdate = 2016-11-18 | format = PDF }}</ref>整场飓风在美国至少夺走26条人命<ref>{{cite report | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141018034515/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pastdeadlya1.html | archivedate = 2014-10-18 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pastdeadlya1.html | title = The Deadliest Atlantic Tropical Cyclones, 1492 – Present | author1 = Jack Beven | author2 = Jose F. Partagas | author3 = Edward N. Rappaport | date = 1997-04-22 | work = National Hurricane Center | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | accessdate = 2014-10-18 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。
